room_title: Escape room "Game Master" by Escape Room Ft Myers in Fort Myers
room_address: 9280 College Pkwy Suite 7, Fort Myers, FL 33919
room_description: You have awakened to find that the sick mastermind has drugged you, chained you up and locked you up in his bathroom. You are the new game pawns in his sick twisted game, and you have the face the ultimate test. You have 60 minutes to prove that your life is worth more than those sacrifices before you. You have no choice, you must escape!
